Task 023b's intent was contingent on 023's finding, then made concrete by its own spec goal: "**AlphaProbe must not export algebraic-looking alpha classifications unless the finite-window evidence is both numerically non-boundary and nested-window stable enough for downstream composition.**" — i.e. add the `alpha_zero_boundary` and `alpha_unstable_window` strata plus nested-window stability evidence so the instrument stops over-claiming (`Agent_tasks/Completed/codex_task023b_alphaprobe_reliability_evidence.md` L36-45, confidence high).

